entries.title_d: Command wants you to patrol the area looking for Rebel activity while they inspect the data you recovered.
entries.title: Endor System: Patrol the Endor System
entries.split_quest_alert: Calling all Imperial pilots. 3rd TIE Wing has encountered heavy Rebel resistance. All available pilots are to proceed immediately to the following location.
entries.quest_patrol_d: When you reach a navigation waypoint you will receive a new one to the next location. Follow the patrol waypoints until you come to the end of your patrol.
entries.quest_location_d: Remain in the Endor system and follow the patrol navigation waypoints. As you reach one navigation waypoint, you will get a new waypoint to the next location on the patrol route.
